    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Chat HILT status mix over time",
      "description": "Status counters from RecordGuardrailEvaluation(\"openclaw:hilt\", action). Stack shows requested vs approved/denied/timeout/unsupported simultaneously so you can see the operator-response funnel.\n\ncovered_by:\n  - defenseclaw_guardrail_evaluations \u2192 internal/telemetry/metrics.go (RecordGuardrailEvaluation)",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "defenseclaw-prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 12,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 8
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (severity) (rate(defenseclaw_connector_hook_outcome_total{connector=~\"$connector\", would_block=\"true\"}[$__rate_interval])) or vector(0)",
          "legendFormat": "{{severity}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "cps",
          "custom": {
            "stacking": {
              "mode": "normal"
            },
            "fillOpacity": 25
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Chat HILT approval-vs-denial rate (1h rolling)",
      "description": "approved / (approved + denied + timeout). Slow drift toward 0 means operators are denying more often \u2014 investigate via the verdict-categories panel on Security.\n\ncovered_by:\n  - defenseclaw_guardrail_evaluations \u2192 internal/telemetry/metrics.go (RecordGuardrailEvaluation)",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "defenseclaw-prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 12,
        "y": 12,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 8
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (action) (rate(defenseclaw_inspect_evaluations_total{tool=~\"$connector:.*\", action=~\"allow|block|confirm\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "approval rate",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percentunit",
          "min": 0,
          "max": 1
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Pending requests gauge (5m window)",
      "description": "Approximation of in-flight requests = requested - (approved + denied + timeout) summed over the last 5 minutes. Sustained positive value means operators are slow to respond. Negative or zero means the queue is clear.\n\ncovered_by:\n  - defenseclaw_guardrail_evaluations \u2192 internal/telemetry/metrics.go (RecordGuardrailEvaluation)",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "defenseclaw-prometheus"
